The building received several awards such as the British Council for School Environment award under the category ‘Inspire Design-Special Needs’ in 2008 and the ‘Project of the Year’ and ‘Best Value’ Award at the South West Built Environment Award.', N'Access to the piece is by appointment, please contact the school to arrange a visit.', NULL, 80, 300, NULL, 70, N'Roof light grilles: good
