(N'MN164', N'Welcome to Welton Primary School', N'Welcome to Welton Primary School is a large rectangular shaped piece of colourful mosaic made of three separate pieces, with square mirror insets and the words ‘Welcome to Welton Primary School’ spelt out.', 2005, 2005, NULL, N'Children created their own small mosaic mirror to add to the larger mural', N'Mosaic', N'Welcome to Welton Primary School', N'The artist worked with the children and the teachers.', N'Access to the piece is by appointment, please contact the school to arrange a visit.
See also David Bowers’ Welcome to Bath City Farm at Bath City Farm Bath. 
